snippet.title: Amber Heard is getting CANCELLED??
snippet.description:
Amber  Heard may be looking at an expanded job for DC also. Going ahead there have been tales that she will see an expanded job in the establishment. It could begin with this next film after she saw some more screen time in Zack Snyder's Justice League delivered a couple of months prior. While there are a lot of people out there calling for Amber Heard to get a retraction, it doesn't appear to be working. Indeed, even with the steady Twitter moving and petitions, the studios don't show up all that worried about the advertising hits.
